.TH BERYL 1 "Feb 2020" "beryl"
.SH NAME
beryl
\- a primitive DNS nameserver.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B beryl
[\fIoptions\fP]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints total number of threads on the machine and date/time in the local
timezone to the standard output.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v\fR
print version
.TP
\fB\-h\fR
show help message
